Thanks EZTV,  Been a fan of yours for a few yrs now,  But what is going on with your site?    I only dl episodes of programs I really like due to the time lag between the states and uk.  Take Dexter for instance UK is One whole year behind   Is this fair, I think not   And this is my pledge I will stop downloading as soon as these programs reach us at the same time or just several hours behind.   I feel like a second rate citizen compared to the states and other countries who get all the good shows first.   After all I am paying for a service which is not giving me the same goods as it is to someone else (or several million people) so for now I can only Dl the shows I love and hope that I dont end up in jail for being a second rate citizen.
